  "name": "Dissonant Whispers",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>One creature of your choice that you can see within range hears a discordant melody in its mind. The target makes a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, it takes [[/damage 3d6 psychic]] damage and must immediately use its Reaction, if available, to move as far away from you as it can, using the safest route. On a successful save, the target takes half as much damage only. A &amp;Reference[deafened apply=false] creature automatically succeeds on the save.</p><p><strong>Using a Higher-Level Spell Slot.</strong> The damage increases by 1d6 for each spell slot level above 1.</p>",
